1348
02:44:51,500 --> 02:44:53,500
We must do this.

1349
02:44:53,500 --> 02:45:08,000
We must pass this bill and help our counties deal with the cost of keeping these facilities in good working order and to upgrade with the codes and guidelines.

1350
02:45:08,000 --> 02:45:23,000
